{"Id":598729,"Title":"和劝农六章","Dynasty":"明","Author":"陈履","Context":"天职生物，地职养人。裁成辅相，职为圣真。兹曰三才，一理所因。地平天成，我思古人。亩亩高原，宜尔黍稷。眷此泽国，嘉稻斯殖。惟水利农，亦以害穑。水患既蠲，民乃可食。余起海滨，跋涉川陆。帝命来吴，令佐熙穆。官守不恪，焉逭斥逐。是用虚怀，询于耆宿。众靡惮劳，劳暂逸久。联尔比邻，结尔同耦。固尔堤防，易尔田亩。谋则协心，作则胼手。农夫望岁，冀勿空匮。无鳏厥官，时余所冀。百川告驯，灾害不至。庶免素餐，祛我中愧。莫匪王事，农务奚鄙。宗伯硕人，实迪余履。通力合作，选农遗轨。尔众听之，嘉言洵美。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"95c4991f26d0c0d61f6bb17dc5d44556","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6805468,"Sentence":"天职生物，地职养人。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"tiān zhǐ shēng wù ，地zhǐ yǎng rén ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6805469,"Sentence":"裁成辅相，职为圣真。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"cái chéng fǔ xiāng ，zhǐ wéi shèng zhēn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6805470,"Sentence":"兹曰三才，一理所因。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"cǐ yuē sān cái ，yī li suǒ yīn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6805471,"Sentence":"地平天成，我思古人。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"地pǐng tiān chéng ，wǒ sāi gǔ rén ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6805472,"Sentence":"亩亩高原，宜尔黍稷。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mǔ mǔ gāo yuán ，yǐ ěr shǔ jì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6805473,"Sentence":"眷此泽国，嘉稻斯殖。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"juàn ci zé guó ，jiā dào sī 殖","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6805474,"Sentence":"惟水利农，亦以害穑。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wéi shui lì nóng ，yì yi hài sè ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6805475,"Sentence":"水患既蠲，民乃可食。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shui huàn jì juān ，mǐn nǎi kě shǐ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6805476,"Sentence":"余起海滨，跋涉川陆。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yú qi hǎi bīn ，bá shè chuān lìu ","Tag":null,"Explanatio